==English==

===Etymology===
* From {{etyl|enm}}.
* {{suffix|absolute|ly}}

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/æb.səˈluːt.li/}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˌæb.sə.ˈlut.li/|/ˈæb.sə.ˌlut.li/}}
* {{audio|en-us-absolutely.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}

# In an absolute, independent, or [[unconditional]] manner; [[utterly]], [[positively]], [[wholly]].
# With [[absolution]].
# {{context|grammar}} In a manner that does not take an [[object]].

====Usage notes====
* Absolutely is not to be confused with [[intensive]]s (very, indeed, or others) , as it is an unconditional term.

